{"tid":2024152,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外謀指支那推動支國企業透過滬倫通赴英掛牌","createTime":"2020-05-19T12:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T12:36:04.000Z","uid":75656,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2cd065982a19e9eaea90b43b7b3063bf009e9109","tid":2024152,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T12:23:04.000Z","msg":"外電引述消息指，中國正敦促國內公司到英國倫敦上市，旨在新型肺炎危機後，恢復通過滬倫通上市發行，加強海外聯繫，預期下半年將有1-2間中國公司在倫敦上市。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報道指，中國當局已批准中國太平洋保險和國投電力繼續到倫敦上市的計劃，當中，中國太保很可能成為今年在倫敦交易所亮相的第一間中國公司，正尋求集資20億至30億美元，預期9-10月定價。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指，內地同意中國長江電力開始籌備到倫敦作第二上市，計劃集資約25億美元。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527012-20200519.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527012-20200519.htm&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7v2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=7a61896c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527012-20200519.htm&h=cc3ee355\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527012-20200519.htm</a>"},{"pid":"996115c79068b239245ba1d9d2d35bb583378320","tid":2024152,"uid":75656,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T12:23:37.000Z","msg":"外媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355cb7f60dff73d3b768909ee2c59e593bbec6ff","tid":2024152,"uid":52006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T12:25:10.000Z","msg":"日落國唔係諗住倫敦取代香港做支共白手套下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e147a0219a6cb141e5d970233e7a58a5aa7630","tid":2024152,"uid":24140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T12:25:28.000Z","msg":"英國佬表示 : 請君入甕"},{"pid":"9dc05c82faef44d9d13d16a4de04f409de63b624","tid":2024152,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"355cb7f60dff73d3b768909ee2c59e593bbec6ff","tid":2024152,"uid":52006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"cit